ueenship in Thirteenth-Century England\n  | publisher = Blackwell Publishers\n  | location= Oxford, UK\n  | isbn = 978-0-631-22739-7\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Huscroft\n  | first = Richard\n  | year = 2006\n  | title = Expulsion: England's Jewish solution\n  | publisher = Tempus\n  | location= Stroud, UK\n  | isbn = 978-0-752-43729-3\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Jobson\n  | first = Adrian\n  | year = 2012\n  | title = The First English Revolution: Simon de Montfort, Henry III and the Barons' War\n  | publisher = Bloomsbury\n  | location= London, UK\n  | isbn = 978-1-84725-226-5\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Kalof\n  | first = Linda\n  | year = 2007\n  | title = Looking at Animals in Human History\n  | publisher = Reaktion Books\n  | location= London, UK\n  | isbn = 978-1-86189-334-5\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n*{{cite journal| last=Langmuir |first=Gavin |authorlink=|journal= Speculum|title=The Knight's Tale of Young Hugh of Lincoln|volume= 47|year= 1972|pages=459\u201382 |issn=| ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Lewis\n  | first = Suzanne\n  | year = 1987\n  | title = The Art of Matthew Paris in the Chronica Majora\n  | publisher = University of California Press\n  | location= Berkeley, US and Los Angeles, US\n  | isbn = 978-0-520-04981-9\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Maddicott\n  | first = J. R.\n  | year = 2004\n  | title = Simon de Montfort\n  | publisher = Cambridge University Press\n  | location= Cambridge, UK\n  | isbn = 978-0-521-37636-5\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Maier\n  | first = Christoph T.\n  | year = 2003\n  | title = Preaching the Crusades: Mendicant Friars and the Cross in the Thirteenth Century \n  | edition =\n  | publisher = Cambridge University Press\n  | location= Cambridge, UK\n  | isbn =  978-0-521-63873-9\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Mayr-Harting\n  | first = Henry\n  | year = 2011\n  | title = Religion, Politics and Socie